{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"872f70acd9","title":"转发华北局关于山西省直属机关审干情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6ce0a56e2f","index":0,"year":1951,"month":6,"day":19,"articleId":"872f70acd9"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"2e1bc0f12e","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"872f70acd9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央华北局1951年6月18日转报的山西省直属机关一周审干情况报告。报告谈到山西省直机关审干运动的几点经验：一、加强对小组长的具体领导，更多地了解小组长的疑难问题，帮助小组长做好每个人的思想工作。二、放手使用积极分子，在实际工作中进行培养与锻炼。对积极分子的条件要求不能过高。对积极分子除思想教育外，必须经常分配给他们适当的工作。通过他们联系一批新于部，打破领导上的闭塞情况。三、选择坦白较好的作典型报告，并让大家来评判其彻底与否，这样做对大家的启发作用大。"}],"contents":[{"id":"899a347037","type":"title","text":"转发华北局关于山西省直属机关审干情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"872f70acd9"},{"id":"2e1bc0f12e","type":"paragraph","text":"客中央局，并转分局，省市区党委及地委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"872f70acd9"},{"id":"e12c46e1c5","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将山西省直属机关六月七日审干情况的报告”发给你们，这是一个极好的经验，请你们仿行","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"872f70acd9"},{"id":"5a4c2d72c6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"872f70acd9"},{"id":"9cc4d9c525","type":"paragraph","text":"六月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"872f70acd9"}],"page":{"id":"9771c5dec6","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"872f70acd9","start":380,"end":380}}}},"__N_SSG":true}